{"tid":2151693,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"向水炮車掟磚造成八厘米凹痕 17歲男生認罪還押候判 須賠償9,900元","createTime":"2020-08-11T13:40:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-11T14:28:36.000Z","uid":240362,"like":3,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"bf9815ec3e38c3d72aec31a58db26f0630d0e5a3","tid":2151693,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T13:40:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200811/WUJFA7MHAZN5E7N6JINENX5O6Q/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200811%2FWUJFA7MHAZN5E7N6JINENX5O6Q%2F&d=9ox5Qr7lvCKhSYdyRcf9FoRM%2FwdnRWUJBfohchWxIRY%3D&h=95b02441\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200811%2FWUJFA7MHAZN5E7N6JINENX5O6Q%2F&h=aebfd439\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200811/WUJFA7MHAZN5E7N6JINENX5O6Q/</a><br />\n<br />\n警方於今年元旦腰斬民陣遊行後，出動水炮車在灣仔及銅鑼灣一帶清場，其間17歲男學生向水炮車尾掟磚，旋即被警員制服，並被搜出鎅刀、鎚仔以及易燃劑等物件。男生今承認刑事毀壞及管有物品意圖損壞財產兩罪，控方指水炮車有八厘米的凹痕，要求被告賠償9,900元維修費。主任裁判官錢禮先索取被告的一系列報告，將案押後至8月25日判刑，其間被告須還柙候判。"},{"pid":"2b6d281cdf6d7a3bec85426bef698bd1afdb4c57","tid":2151693,"uid":105340,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T13:41:22.000Z","msg":"我地幫你陪"},{"pid":"d5c3bdbd81aa4ecc71d46dd660049f7ab02bf3f6","tid":2151693,"uid":12558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T13:42:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/